    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been well-maintained throughout its ownership. The engine and transmission operate smoothly, and the interior is clean with only minor signs of regular use. While there are a few small exterior blemishes typical of a pre-owned car, it remains mechanically sound and ready for its next owner. It offers a reliable driving experience and has recently undergone a standard service check.",
