    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a dependable ride with plenty of character? This well-loved vehicle is ready for its next chapter! While it shows some honest wear and tear from its years of service, it remains a solid, functional choice for anyone seeking reliable transportation at a great value. It's a practical, honest car that still has plenty of life left in it!",
